{"tid":1965470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強指元朗721事件當晚除白衣人打人　亦有黑衣人作襲擊","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T14:10:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7a79454a5267f1923f06bc58e9fe06594362bb","tid":1965470,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局局長李家超在立法會財委會特別會議說，警隊來年開支預算258億元是經過保安局審批，有實際需要。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強首次提到元朗721襲擊事件當晚，除了白衣人打人，亦有黑衣人作出襲擊，兩方面都會調查。<br />\n<br />\n立法會財委會討論財政預算案保安方面的開支，警隊繼續是焦點。<br />\n<br />\n有議員指，警員最近在示威現場，要求互不認識的人站在一起，以他們涉嫌違反限聚令作出調查，批評警方執法不公。有議員要求警方更詳細交代最近領取超時工作津貼的情況。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月港台記者在北角被人打傷手，他最近接獲警方通知已經結案，沒有任何人被捕，鄧炳強在會後說不是每宗案件都有充分證據會作出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n他又指涉及反修例示威訓斥警員的宗數，增加1宗至22宗，當中4宗亦正進行紀律覆檢，其餘18宗經投訴警察課處理。"},{"pid":"7e53d539fa0da734d0e6e2f97835adde80a1d08b","tid":1965470,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=387319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387319&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=ebcc42e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387319&h=4c783645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=387319</a>"},{"pid":"9ee0f83c02c815fd072af75568bd8a2a9e064d8b","tid":1965470,"uid":128873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"一齊拉咪得鳩up 做咩？"},{"pid":"adac62d0efda21ca49f2ee88b98075c6bcbfce0a","tid":1965470,"uid":64337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"又想玩偽造證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999caa9379c40c8165933ac3e588b3204fa5be0e","tid":1965470,"uid":15084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"rep